      <title>对冲基金抢购日本利率交易商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-23/hedge-funds-snap-up-japan-rates-traders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社获悉，过去 18 个月，十多名日本利率交易员离开银行，转投对冲基金，因为他们押注日本央行放松刺激措施将带来波动性推动的交易热潮。丽莎杜在彭博电视台报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-23/hedge-funds-snap-up-japan-rates-traders</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 01:26:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>First Sentier 以低收费关闭 90 亿美元基金并裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/first-sentier-shuts-four-funds-with-9-billion-30-staff-to-go</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚基金管理公司 First Sentier Investors 周二宣布，计划关闭四支总额达 140 亿澳元（合 90 亿美元）的基金，退出低利润业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/first-sentier-shuts-four-funds-with-9-billion-30-staff-to-go</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 01:17:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
